Interface Filter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Adaptable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Marked, Marked, ModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Base64Impl, FilterImpl, InterpolatorImpl, MarkdownImpl
    public interface Filter
extends ModelElement
    A representation of the model object 'Filter'. Base class for filters which take an object, adapt to ${javadoc/org.nasdanika.common.SupplierFactory}, obtain a stream and produce another stream from it.

    The following features are supported:
